songs.title: Naked Muse
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
I wake up to your body bathed in orange light
I wake up to your body framed in that golden square of light

[Chorus]
It makes it, it feels
It makes it, it feels
It makes it, it feels
Like we're a long way from home

[Chorus]
Naked muse
Naked muse
Naked muse who makes her own music


[Chorus]
It makes it, it feels
It makes it, it feels
It makes it, it feels
Like we’ll never be this free again

[Verse 2]
She's not on the prowl, she doesn't want to be chased
She’s not on the prowl, she doesn't want to be chased
She's not on the prowl, she doesn't want to be chased

[Chorus]
Naked muse
Naked muse
Naked muse makes her own rock 'n' roll music
